   - `analyticsLoadTypes()` now calls `analyticsResume()` instead of
     `analyticsLoadLatest()` directly, so a re-opened page rejoins an in-progress
     run.
   - `analyticsCompute()` refactored to use `_setAnalysisBusy()`.

